        <abstract>
            <p>Advises correspondent on adopting a career; "each person shd. follow his natural bent &amp; improve his special abilities".</p> 
<p>Strongly recommends study of J. S. Mill’s <hi rend="italic">Logic</hi>.</p>  
<p>His own zeal for science was most stimulated by Herschel’s <hi rend="italic">Introduction to the study of natural philosophy</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
